/**
 * The Thesis section â€” cream background.
 * The insight explained in 3-4 sentences.
 */
---

<section class="thesis section-cream section" aria-labelledby="thesis-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="label reveal">The Insight</p>
    <h2 id="thesis-heading" class="thesis-heading reveal">
      AI makes work more human, not less.
    </h2>
    <div class="thesis-body reveal">
      <p>
        When AI handles the grunt work, people collaborate more. They attend to
        details that matter. They build better things. The human part of work
        gets bigger, not smaller.
      </p>
      <p>
        AI is an amplifier. In the right hands, it does amazing things. But the
        right hands need the right environment: trust, standards, transparency,
        and a way of working that keeps humans in control of the things that
        matter.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a href="/about" class="thesis-link link">
      The story behind the mission
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .thesis-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .thesis-body {
    max-width: var(--max-width-prose);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .thesis-body p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .thesis-body p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .thesis-link {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
